These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, july
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, cranberry, pepper
House: colonial, farmhouse, cottage
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, reggae
1. the person eating cranberry is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the colonial house is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the person eating pepper##1
7. the cottage house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Birthday      | july  | march       | september   |
| Food          | pepper | cauliflower | cranberry |
| House         | colonial  | cottage | farmhouse    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | blues       | folk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, potato, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, indie, funk
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, boat, subway
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, snake
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Food          | pear      | potato  | radish        |
| Music-Genre         | funk | indie | techno |
| Transport   | scooter | boat | subway       |
| Pet           | snake     | rat     | hedgehog      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, dancer, software-developer
House: craftsman, cape-cod, modern
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, rowing
1. the software-developer is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the modern house is in the middle##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | almond-milk        | mirinda |
| Job           | dancer    | software-developer | chef    |
| House   | craftsman | modern             | cape-cod  |
| Sport     | rowing     | parkour                | cricket  |

