.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pepper, tomato
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, old-henry, havana
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the person eating pear is the fan of rock##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | pepper    | tomato  | pear      |
| Game           | backgammon    | mah-jongg | billiard |
| Cigar   | havana   | old-henry  | dunhill     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | punk    | rock      |

