.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar, blend
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, nurse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, sailing, rowing
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person who's sport is baseball is the fisherman##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the nurse is the blend-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the bongani-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the coach##1
7. the fisherman is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar         | blend | bongani     | bolivar   |
| Job           | nurse       | fisherman   | coach     |
| Sport   | sailing     | baseball | rowing |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

