3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
