.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, woodworking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, family, spy
3 different games are played: bridge, go, monopoly
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, rose
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
2. the person playing monopoly is the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | spy         | family       |
| Game           | bridge      | monopoly      | go         |
| Flower     | aconite      | rose         | balloon-flower          |

