.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
City: rome, edinburgh, hamburg
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, mechanic, software-developer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, snowboarding, lacrosse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the roller##1
4. the accountant is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the software-developer is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| City       | edinburgh            | rome      | hamburg  |
| Job         | software-developer | accountant | mechanic |
| Sport         | skiing               | lacrosse | snowboarding |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

