.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, electrician, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, mystery
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, azure, red
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, march, may
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person who likes red##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | martial-arts | mystery     |
| Color   | ebony   | azure       | red     |
| Birthday           | may    | march         | july        |

