.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, journalist, videographer
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, dog
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, thai
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bolivar, old-henry
1. the thai is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the videographer is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Job           | journalist | videographer | architect |
| Pet   | dog        | hamster       | rabbit     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| Cigar     | old-henry | bolivar          | baccarat      |

