.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, subway, van
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, go
1. the person playing go is the fan of gospel##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Transport   | subway | boat     | van     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel        | folk        |
| Game           | mah-jongg    | go         | snooker     |

