.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, polish
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, wooden
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, punk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the mexican##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the nigerian is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the polish is the cape-cod house##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality         | nigerian | mexican | polish   |
| House           | wooden     | farmhouse    | cape-cod   |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | punk    | dubstep   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

