.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-14::.
City: edinburgh, boston, london
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, strawberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, traveling
There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, colombian
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the german##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person traveling to london is the colombian##1
6. the malaysian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| City    | edinburgh | boston     | london      |
| Food        | garlic | lime       | strawberry |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | german   | colombian  |

