There 3 different types of food: artichoke, kale, peas
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, social-worker, videographer
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, purple, pink
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the videographer##1
3. the person who likes purple is the firefighter##1
4. the firefighter is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person eating peas is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | almond-milk | cola       |
| Food          | peas     | artichoke   | kale       |
| Job         | firefighter  | videographer   | social-worker |
| Color   | purple   | pink       | lilac  |

