.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, sailing
There 3 different types of food: mango, pear, peas
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, horse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Sport      | sailing      | parkour    | badminton    |
| Food          | peas         | pear    | mango   |
| Pet           | dog | horse | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | d&b     | folk    |

