The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, weightlifting
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: british, pakistani, russian
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the russian is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Flower      | sunflower  | zinnia   | lily  |
| Sport          | rowing   | weightlifting | badminton   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco      | rock    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | british    | russian |

