.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, tea
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, azure, blood-red
There 3 different types of food: tomato, strawberry, garlic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | juice         | tea     | coffee     |
| Color           | azure        | blood-red | red |
| Food   | strawberry        | garlic   | tomato    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

