.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, potato, tomato
City: nizza, london, paris
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, quad-bike
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, water-polo
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | tomato     | potato    | avocado    |
| City         | nizza | paris | london     |
| Transport   | scooter  | motorbike      | quad-bike        |
| Sport         | handball   | surfing   | water-polo |

 